## Section 6: Healthcare & Enterprise Operations Context

### Why This Matters in Healthcare IT

Healthcare environments require:
- Strict access control
- Auditable change history
- Minimal disruption
- Regulatory defensibility (HIPAA, HITECH)

Configuration Management ensures:
- Systems remain compliant
- Access changes are justified
- Admin activity is controlled

This directly supports:
- Tier 2 / Tier 2.5 security operations
- IAM oversight roles
- Compliance and audit functions

---

### What This Shows

- You understand **real-world enterprise IT**
- You recognize healthcare-specific risk
- You can operate in regulated environments

